类 StartController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.StartController

  • public class StartController
extends java.lang.Object
    Class controller.StartingController is the Controller Class of 'SettingPage.fxml'.

    provided by IOException, ActionEvent, FXML, ActionEvent, ActionEvent and Main.

    This is the controller class for page the game starting page. Actions are supervised and reacted in this class. user can launch the game by clicking the start button.

    版本:
    1.03
    作者:
    Boon Giin Lee, Heng Yu, Chen Liao
